title: The Chaos at DC Studios
description:
This video is sponsored by Curiosity Stream. Get both Nebula and Curiosity Stream here:   https://curiositystream.com/captainmidnight for less than $12 a YEAR.
James Gunn made a lot of waves when he took over at DC Studios, and now it looks like he's set to restart the DC universe in a very different way. A way that may not include Wonder Woman 3, Black Adam or Henry Cavill's Superman. I go into all of it here!
